<!-- Case Study Overview -->
<section class="case-study-overview">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="overview-grid">
      <div class="overview-content" data-aos="fade-right">
        <h2>About the Client</h2>
        <p>The 22q Family Foundation is a non-profit organization dedicated to supporting families affected by 22q11.2 deletion syndrome, a genetic disorder that can cause a wide range of health problems including heart defects, immune system abnormalities, and developmental delays.</p>
        <p>The foundation provides resources, education, and support to families, healthcare providers, and educators to improve the lives of those affected by 22q.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="overview-stats" data-aos="fade-left">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">65%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Increase in Online Donations</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">40%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Reduction in Administrative Time</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">80%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Improved Data Utilization</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">3x</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Increase in Email Engagement</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Challenge Section -->
<section class="case-study-section bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Challenge</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="challenge-grid">
        <div class="challenge-content" data-aos="fade-right">
          <p>When the 22q Family Foundation approached us, they were facing several operational challenges that were hampering their ability to fulfill their mission effectively:</p>
          <ul class="challenge-list">
            <li>
              <h3>Manual Data Management</h3>
              <p>The team was spending countless hours manually entering donor information, tracking contributions, and managing supporter communications using spreadsheets and disconnected systems.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h3>Limited Donor Insights</h3>
              <p>With data spread across multiple platforms, the foundation struggled to gain a complete picture of their donors, limiting their ability to personalize outreach and recognize recurring supporters.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h3>Inefficient Event Management</h3>
              <p>The foundation hosts several fundraising events annually, but lacked an integrated system to manage registrations, track attendance, and follow up with participants.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <h3>Disjointed Communication</h3>
              <p>Without a centralized database, the team faced challenges in coordinating volunteer activities, donor communications, and educational outreach programs.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="challenge-image" data-aos="fade-left">
          <img src="/images/case-studies/challenge-illustration.svg" alt="Challenges Illustration" width="500" height="400">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Solution Section -->
<section class="case-study-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Solution</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="solution-grid reverse">
        <div class="solution-image" data-aos="fade-right">
          <img src="/images/case-studies/solution-illustration.svg" alt="Solution Illustration" width="500" height="400">
        </div>
        <div class="solution-content" data-aos="fade-left">
          <p>After a thorough assessment of the foundation's needs, we implemented a comprehensive CRM solution tailored specifically for non-profit organizations:</p>
          
          <div class="solution-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-database"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Centralized Donor Database</h3>
              <p>We implemented a cloud-based CRM system that consolidated all donor information, donation history, and communication records into a single, secure database accessible to authorized staff from anywhere.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="solution-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Customized Reporting & Analytics</h3>
              <p>We set up tailored dashboards and automated reports to provide real-time insights into donation trends, campaign performance, and donor demographics, enabling data-driven decision making.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="solution-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Integrated Event Management</h3>
              <p>We implemented an event management module that streamlined registration, payment processing, and attendee tracking, while automatically updating the donor database with participation information.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="solution-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Automated Communication Workflows</h3>
              <p>We created personalized email templates and automated communication sequences for donor acknowledgment, event reminders, and educational content distribution, all integrated with the CRM system.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

